Package manager

Class Date

java.lang.Object
manager.Date
All Implemented Interfaces:
Comparable<Date>
public class Date extends Object implements Comparable<Date>
This class handles the Date object which contains day month and year fields and acts as the birthday parameter for a student.
Author:
Raghunandan Wable, Srikumar Avirneni
